Installing:
  1. Download MongoDB: https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/installation/
  2.    (mkdir /data/db)
  3. Run the mongodb database process:
        mongod

Create DB example in json for import in parallel cmd:
cd C:\Program Files\MongoDB\Server\3.2\bin
mongoimport C:\data\db\shops.json --jsonArray --collection shops
mongoimport C:\data\db\products.json --jsonArray --collection products

Gson converter: https://github.com/google/gson



  https://github.com/sedouard/mongodb-mva